text: Akaa is a city in Finland. About 17,000 people live there. Nearby municipalities include Hämeenlinna, Lempäälä, Urjala, Valkeakoski and Vesilahti. In Akaa is the biggest mämmi factory in world. There were mämmi- eating competitions in 2005 and 2007. ==Other websites== * Community website Category:Cities in Finland Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
